  "detailed_description": "<h1>TRADING CARDS</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425250/extras/9c4ef5732d6ca092f3069eb8eaf3a1cc.avif?t=1771601682\" width=612 height=157 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425250/extras/543cb65b82341c0f4f934ceb8f2092ef.avif?t=1771601682\" width=600 height=174 /></span><br>Gravity Field is an innovative space-logic puzzle game that challenges players with time-inverted objects in a gravity-defying world without a discernible top or bottom. The game's minimalist design features cubic rooms containing only essential items that serve specific functions. Players must navigate the walls and ceiling, often utilizing time inversion to solve puzzles of varying degrees of complexity.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425250/extras/426d5c852409d66e007999d0c1666223.poster.avif?t=1771601682\" width=600 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425250/extras/426d5c852409d66e007999d0c1666223.webm?t=1771601682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425250/extras/426d5c852409d66e007999d0c1666223.mp4?t=1771601682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Gravity Fields are found throughout the game, each with its own gravitational direction, affecting players' movements and reactions inside and outside the field. Along the way, players will encounter closed doors, requiring creative problem-solving skills and the use of cubes, buttons, and connectors to unlock them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425250/extras/70ddd22c0227c840df7eece05aa0aa60.poster.avif?t=1771601682\" width=598 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425250/extras/70ddd22c0227c840df7eece05aa0aa60.webm?t=1771601682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425250/extras/70ddd22c0227c840df7eece05aa0aa60.mp4?t=1771601682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The time inversion icon introduces a new level of complexity, allowing players to reverse time for specific objects and solve problems in unique ways. The game lacks a plot, as it is focused on challenging players with increasingly complex puzzles.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425250/extras/9376fbaffc3200a35a9594ad64e27139.poster.avif?t=1771601682\" width=600 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425250/extras/9376fbaffc3200a35a9594ad64e27139.webm?t=1771601682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425250/extras/9376fbaffc3200a35a9594ad64e27139.mp4?t=1771601682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Gravity Field is a must-play for puzzle enthusiasts, featuring a wide range of levels and tasks that unlock new challenges with each successful completion. Get ready to defy gravity and test your puzzle-solving skills like never before!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425250/extras/0766c05086666c42369c6fcc0493e90c.poster.avif?t=1771601682\" width=600 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425250/extras/0766c05086666c42369c6fcc0493e90c.webm?t=1771601682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425250/extras/0766c05086666c42369c6fcc0493e90c.mp4?t=1771601682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
