1682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425250/extras/70ddd22c0227c840df7eece05aa0aa60.mp4?t=1771601682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The time inversion icon introduces a new level of complexity, allowing players to reverse time for specific objects and solve problems in unique ways. The game lacks a plot, as it is focused on challenging players with increasingly complex puzzles.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425250/extras/9376fbaffc3200a35a9594ad64e27139.poster.avif?t=1771601682\" width=600 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425250/extras/9376fbaffc3200a35a9594ad64e27139.webm?t=1771601682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425250/extras/9376fbaffc3200a35a9594ad64e27139.mp4?t=1771601682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Gravity Field is a must-play for puzzle enthusiasts, featuring a wide range of levels and tasks that unlock new challenges with each successful completion. Get ready to defy gravity and test your puzzle-solving skills like never before!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425250/extras/0766c05086666c42369c6fcc0493e90c.poster.avif?t=1771601682\" width=600 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425250/extras/0766c05086666c42369c6fcc0493e90c.webm?t=1771601682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425250/extras/0766c05086666c42369c6fcc0493e90c.mp4?t=1771601682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
